<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=025b37db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=ce9af751\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1214bd94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=c18277bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=64d1632d\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=3c1efb2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b1c65a0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"51a27decd299f8b6ed5aadc89bf8ba66909d0dc9","tid":1263994,"uid":258976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"唔好通頂啦<br />\n養足精神71 朝早去"},{"pid":"93bc7b29e78b755eb914cc7ab79532883975fffa","tid":1263994,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"不舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0666e44cd629bcd27d8a42f4d872e856db9e6cc1","tid":1263994,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:14:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04acb67ced68102e804104d852dce1f0219bf885","tid":1263994,"uid":180265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T22:20:52.000Z","msg":"驚挨唔到咁耐 <img src=\"/a